Interface DataTypeVisitor<R>

  • Type Parameters:
    R - result type
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DataTypeDefaultVisitor, DataTypeToLogicalType, FastHash.FastHashVisitor, FieldWriterFactory, HilbertIndexer.TypeVisitor, InternalRowToSizeVisitor, ReassignFieldId, ZIndexer.TypeVisitor

    @Public
public interface DataTypeVisitor<R>
    The visitor definition of DataType. The visitor transforms a data type into instances of R.
